tative data collection was used to examine relevant documents and literature, and a deep semi-structured interview tool. The research questions were analyzed using Attride and  Sterling theme analysis technique Based on this, four main themes (15 themes) were arranged (later) from 89 themes (components) related to the model for evaluating the implementation of human resources development policies of the Government of the Islamic Republic of Iran. To validate the extraction factors Of the three stages of Delphi, 76 of the components were confirmed and 13 of them were rejected
